episodes.title: Danger Island: Strange Pilot
episodes.plot: Archer inserts himself into a domestic dispute and engine troubles threaten to ruin his business.

episodes.title: Danger Island: Disheartening Situation
episodes.plot: Archer works to overcome his dead stick while Pam and those who bailed try to survive the local nightlife.

episodes.title: Danger Island: Different Modes of Preparing the Fruit
episodes.plot: Archer and Pam look for ways to make enough money to repair the plane.

episodes.title: Danger Island: A Warrior in Costume
episodes.plot: A group of German pilots show up on the island. Their leader was Archer's nemesis during the Spanish Civil War, shooting Archer down a total of five times. Archer longs for revenge.

episodes.title: Danger Island: Strange Doings in the Taboo Groves
episodes.plot: But there is no joy in Mudville- mighty Pam has struck out.

episodes.title: Danger Island: Some Remarks on Cannibalism
episodes.plot: Archer and Pam try to escape the cannibals with the less-than-willing help of an anthropologist while everyone else races to the idol.

episodes.title: Danger Island: Comparative Wickedness of Civilized and Unenlightened Peoples
episodes.plot: Archer helps defend a village from party crashers intent on ruining oysterfest.

episodes.title: Danger Island: A Discovery
episodes.plot: The Band finally closes on a discovery.
